item.description:
The Official NHC COED Softball Team will be holding a team meeting on Thursday evening at 5pm at Humphrey's East Restaurant, 175 Humphrey St. in New Haven.

I tried to pick a casual spot that has parking, since finding parking downtown at 5pm sucks.

Please make every effort to attend Thursday to sign the roster and make the $60 season payment. I need to get payment and roster information in to the league THIS WEEK!

I will be there from 5pm until at least 7pm.

If you cannot attend, and are on the team, please contact me ASAP to make other arrangements.

If you have any questions, feel free to contact me via email or phone,

Humphrey's East Website
item.name: NHC COED SOFTBALL TEAM MEETING
